### Working Model: {{WORKING_MODEL}}

{{#if WORKING_MODEL_HUB_CENTRIC}}
**Hub-centric:** This hub is the starting point for all work. Projects are created here AND worked on from here. Memory, skills, and planning stay centralized. Projects get lighter scaffolding — constitutional content inline, but no copied skills (run /bos from hub).
{{/if}}
{{#if WORKING_MODEL_PROJECT_CENTRIC}}
